subject: Basketball
Draft and Recruitment (Sports)
lead_paragraph: The Milwaukee Bucks have signed the second-round draft pick Darington Hobson, a 6-foot-7, 210-pound junior out of New Mexico, who was taken 37th over all in this year’s draft.
